Package gui.gamehome

Class Match

java.lang.Object
gui.gamehome.Match
All Implemented Interfaces:
Gui
public class Match extends Object implements Gui
Match class implements the Gui interface and represents the Match screen of the game. It displays information about different teams in the game.
